../../CHAIN-HISTORY.md:29:Failure in Chain 01 is highly informative. If the explicit remote-shell model shows that the surviving pressure quantity stays comparable to shell energy, then one more plausible exit from the De Giorgi bottleneck is closed with a precise reason. That immediately sharpens the research landscape.
