../../planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:55:The warning is justified. The mission already carries strong negative information about the vorticity route and Beltrami fragility, so a loose rerun would risk spending budget on already-prefigured dead ends.
../../planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:71:The attacker is right that "where the localization cost lands" is the whole problem. Two rewrites with the same headline scaling can differ materially in commutator losses, projector placement, or shell bookkeeping. If those are not itemized, the chain will overstate sameness or improvement.
