+
+- Choosing `coefficient shrinkage in the fixed localized balance` as the gain
+  currency prevented derivative/exponent language from drifting into identity-
+  level cosmetics.
+- The most useful novelty claim was procedural and bounded: the value of this
+  step is freezing one auditable rewrite table, not pretending a new mechanism
+  has already been found.
+- When the local record already predicts a negative baseline, the shortlist
+  still matters. A narrow candidate family turns "likely collapse" into a
+  future earned statement rather than a prejudice.
