+   geometry branch.
+3. What solution class and theorem-hypothesis compatibility constraints the
+   local repository already forces for that architecture, including any
+   circularity or package-mismatch risks.
+4. What localization protocol is fairest for comparing exact reformulations of
+   the same quadratic nonlinearity without hidden architecture drift.
+5. Which exact reformulation family the local record already suggests as the
+   natural bounded family for this chain, and what each item's likely leverage
